# shared

**Type Property**

The shared print-interaction controller object.

## Declaration

```swift
@MainActor class var shared: UIPrintInteractionController { get }
```

## Return Value

The singleton instance of the `UIPrintInteractionController` class or `nil` if the object could not be created.
